data.description: Great investment property for sale. Built in 1890, this 6 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms Multi-family property at 21 23 George St, Putnam, CT 06260 is approximately 1993 square feet. Investors and Occupant owners come check out this well kept duplex in the heart of Putnam. Units are on different floors. Stop paying rent and start collecting rent. 3 Bedrooms in each unit along with 1 bath each. So many possibilities. City water and City sewer. Sold as is.
